data.description: One of the most magnificent lots in Paradise Valley situated on the south slope of Mummy Mountain. Welcome to unique luxury living in this 4 bed, 3 bath, 4,759sf signature home  on 1.26 Acres with stunning Camelback views! Enter into this contemporary home with panoramic views from every room & high-quality details continue throughout.  Spacious & bright formal living room, open to the formal dining room, and into the eat-in-kitchen w/ an island, and top appliances.  Family room w/ fireplace and wet bar. XL Master suite includes a luxurious feel through the beautiful scenic views, private patio access, full bathroom w/ his & her sinks/vanities....(READ MORE) ... , stylish stand-alone shower & tub, large walk-in closet. The comforts & luxury continue into the 2 guest bedrooms.  The large 3rd guest bedroom can be used as a bedroom, office, game room, gym or all of the above. Relax, entertain & enjoy the tranquil privacy of the backyard, which is more like the 'center' yard as the home surrounds it - featuring built-in BBQ kitchenette w/ refrigerator, xl stone patio, sparkling circular pool & spa w/ breathtaking mountain views! The surrounding land is beautiful desert landscaping - room for expansion of custom garage for the car collector or significant guest house. Beautifully maintained, pride of ownership. Wonderful opportunity for your contemporary home dreams in the heart of Paradise Valley.
